iners()` count, then spawn shortfall; per-spawn the GitHub JIT-config API call (github::generate_jitconfig in start_one, docker_backend.rs:66-101) happens before `docker run`, giving a multi-second TOCTOU window. A foreground `ezgha serve`/`ezgha start` and the installed service instance can both observe alive=0 and both spawn `count` runners.\n\n4. The e2e evidence bundle (evidence/e2e-20260703: init/doctor/start/status/job-run) never exercises `stop` or the installed service, so it provides no counter-evidence.\n\nSeverity: \"major\" is reasonable, not inflated \u2014 a tool whose selling point is host safety/isolation has a stop command that silently fails to stop when the recommended (`install-service` is a headline README feature) deployment mode is used. Not refuted on any ground.", "refuted": false}, "caller": {"type": "direct"}}], "stop_reason": "tool_use", "stop_sequence": null, "stop_details": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 2, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 1376, "cache_read_input_tokens": 69583, "output_tokens": 1580, "server_tool_use": {"web_search_requests": 0, "web_fetch_requests": 0}, "service_tier": "standard", "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 1376}, "inference_geo": "not_available", "iterations": [{"input_tokens": 2, "output_tokens": 1580, "cache_read_input_tokens": 69583, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 1376, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 1376, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "type": "message"}], "speed": "standard"}, "diagnostics": null}, "requestId": "req_011CcfuREHY1FvEdirJw2174", "attributionAgent": "workflow-subagent", "type": "assistant", "uuid": "59d6762f-6629-4f0e-a5cc-52a62402a346", "timestamp": "2026-07-03T22:22:23.677Z", "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/home/jleechan/projects/worktree_runner", "sessionId": "8ca589dd-8422-44b1-a543-52bd7b71f14b", "version": "2.1.198", "gitBranch": "fix/linux-runner-pre-job-hook", "slug": "velvet-wishing-cake"}
